    <item>
      <title>OfficeMax A-Z Index</title>
      <link>http://konigi.com/interface/officemax-z-index/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Jun 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://konigi.com/interface/officemax-z-index/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;OfficeMax displays an a-z index of the store directory in the global navigation. When users hover over any of the letters, a page-wide flyout menu appears to display entries. Clicking on one of the letters, displays the same listing of entries in full page view.&lt;/p&gt;
